---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import CTABanner from '../components/CTABanner.astro';
---
<PageLayout title="WORKS - AI SOLUTION" description="헤세드코퍼레이션의 AI 솔루션 프로젝트 포트폴리오">
  <Hero dark={false} eyebrow="WORKS" title="AI SOLUTION" subtitle="AI 솔루션 프로젝트 포트폴리오" />
  <section class="portfolio">
    <div class="portfolio-inner">
      <div class="portfolio-grid">
        <div class="port-card">
          <div class="port-thumb"></div>
          <div class="port-info">
            <span class="port-tag">AI CONTENT PRODUCTION</span>
            <span class="port-client">클라이밍장</span>
            <h3 class="port-title">AI 홍보영상 제작</h3>
            <p class="port-desc">AI 영상 생성 기술을 활용한 클라이밍장 홍보 영상. 촬영 없이 AI만으로 몰입감 있는 영상 콘텐츠를 완성하여 마케팅 비용을 대폭 절감.</p>
            <span class="port-year">2026</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="port-card">
          <div class="port-thumb"></div>
          <div class="port-info">
            <span class="port-tag">AI WORKFLOW AUTOMATION</span>
            <span class="port-client">HESEDCORP</span>
            <h3 class="port-title">Hesed Dynasty — 자체 AI 조직 구축</h3>
            <p class="port-desc">10개 부서를 커버하는 AI 에이전트 조직을 설계하고 운영. 기획부터 법무까지 실무에 투입하여 AI와 사람이 함께 일하는 업무 프로세스를 실증.</p>
            <span class="port-year">2026</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="coming-soon">More projects coming soon.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <CTABanner title="프로젝트를 함께 만들어요" buttonText="CONTACT US" buttonHref="/contact" />
</PageLayout>
<style>
  .portfolio { padding: 72px 20px; }
  .portfolio-inner { max-width: var(--content-max); margin: 0 auto; }
  .portfolio-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
  .port-card { border-radius: var(--r-md); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06); transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; }
  .port-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
  .port-thumb { height: 240px; background: var(--hc-gray-50); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); font-size: 14px; }
  .port-info { padding: 20px; }
  .port-tag { display: inline-block; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--hc-navy); background: rgba(0, 54, 104, 0.08); padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .port-client { display: block; font-size: 12px; color: var(--hc-orange); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.3px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .port-title { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; margin: 6px 0; color: var(--hc-ink); }
  .port-desc { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgba(0,0,0,0.56); margin: 8px 0 12px; }
  .port-year { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(0,0,0,0.48); }
  .coming-soon { text-align: center; color: rgba(0,0,0,0.32); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 40px; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .portfolio-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
